Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.01,0:23:31.01,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20\fad(540,0)}下集  「邮件的真相」
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-----OPlrcJPN-----
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.73,0:01:35.36,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}憧れを書きとめて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.49,0:01:38.11,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}いつか叶える日のために
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.20,0:01:43.58,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}折り目つけたあのページを　開きたい時がきた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.62,0:01:48.92,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}巻き起こるアレコレで　見失うこともあるけれど
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.00,0:01:51.67,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}ねっ、大丈夫　踏み出してる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.71,0:01:54.30,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}はじまりは想定外
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.46,0:01:57.09,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}君が消せないまま残した
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.17,0:01:59.84,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}寂しがりだった記憶さえ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.89,0:02:03.93,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}読み替えてみせるよ　明るい方へ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.97,0:02:09.35,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}たったそれだけで全てが変わる気がするから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.48,0:02:10.65,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}All Right
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.73,0:02:13.69,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}だから　さあおいで　そのままで！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.73,0:02:16.53,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}弱虫も隠さないで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.65,0:02:17.74,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}"On my Sheep"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.82,0:02:21.41,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}夢乗せ　待ち合わせよう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.57,0:02:27.29,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}この冒険記を綴る中　君の名を呼んでも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.37,0:02:33.79,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}もう迷子じゃない　一緒の旅を始めよう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.88,0:02:41.13,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}そう…きみと、わたし、もっと！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-----OPlrcCHN-----
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.73,0:01:35.36,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}记下你的憧憬
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.49,0:01:38.11,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}以迎接它变成现实的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.20,0:01:43.58,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}折叠起来的书页  正在呼唤着我去翻阅
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.62,0:01:48.92,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}扬起的风沙尘土  可能会让你迷失方向
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.00,0:01:51.67,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}但是不要担心  我们在坚定前行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.71,0:01:54.30,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}只是开端有点意想不到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.46,0:01:57.09,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}你记录下的寂寞经历
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.17,0:01:59.84,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}无法擦去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.89,0:02:03.93,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}但我会解读成未来的财富
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.97,0:02:09.35,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}如此小的努力就能让我感到世界焕然一新
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.48,0:02:10.65,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}All Right
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.73,0:02:13.69,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}所以  跟我来吧  就这样出发！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.73,0:02:16.53,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}没有什么好害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.65,0:02:17.74,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}"On my Sheep"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.82,0:02:21.41,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}放飞梦想  相约明天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.57,0:02:27.29,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}书写这篇历险记的时候  即使呼唤你的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.37,0:02:33.79,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}那也不意味着迷路  而是共同启程的信号
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.88,0:02:41.13,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}没错…你与我 不会停步！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-----EDlrcJPN-----
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.10,0:21:35.41,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}始まりのベル　鍵をかける音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.96,0:21:43.21,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}流れゆく間に大人になる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.48,0:21:48.95,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}走り　はしゃぎ　過ごす日々が
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.31,0:21:53.19,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}遠ざかるときがくる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.51,0:21:57.69,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}ここで出した答えを
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.69,0:22:09.88,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}ああ　どこかで語り継げたら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.69,0:22:15.16,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}迷いながら歩く人波を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.42,0:22:19.49,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}照らし出す光になれるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.62,0:22:28.42,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}揺らぐ空に昇る朝日から一番星まで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.50,0:22:33.10,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}振り返れば懐かしい景色
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.18,0:22:37.40,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}隣には前を向く君が
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.45,0:22:45.62,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}包まれてたグリーンベルトの先
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.79,0:22:53.83,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}続く明日を目指してる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-----EDlrcCHN-----
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.10,0:21:35.41,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}起始之铃  上锁之声
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.96,0:21:43.21,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}在它们的流淌中  我们逐渐成长
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.48,0:21:48.95,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}奔跑欢笑的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.31,0:21:53.19,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}终归会远去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.51,0:21:57.69,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}此刻得出的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.69,0:22:09.88,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}只要将它流传下去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.69,0:22:15.16,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}即使是迷惘而行的人潮
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.42,0:22:19.49,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}也能将其引领
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.62,0:22:28.42,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}从霞光中升起的朝阳  到夜空中闪亮的第一颗星
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.50,0:22:33.10,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}回首望去的景色令人怀念
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.18,0:22:37.40,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}而身旁是望向前方的你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.45,0:22:45.62,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}沿着绿荫大道走下去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.79,0:22:53.83,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}就能到达期望的明天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-----TXT-----
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.47,0:00:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肩膀酸了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.20,0:00:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4月这么忙  还要搞什么庆生会
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.40,0:00:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.27,0:00:21.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是工作的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.46,0:00:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Happy  birthday  to  you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.67,0:00:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Happy  birthday  to  you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.91,0:00:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Happy  birthday  dear  四月出生的同学
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.42,0:00:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Happy  birthday  to  you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.14,0:00:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做这种事有什么意义
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.20,0:00:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  大家笑一笑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.87,0:00:44.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑一笑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.30,0:00:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想一个人读书
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.82,0:00:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生日么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.92,0:01:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}（我绝对选女仆！）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.60,0:01:14.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我要加油  让你黄金周过后也想和我一起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.65,0:01:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是时候给出答案了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.76,0:02:56.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊  那个地方没人住么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.86,0:03:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去就得举手投降了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.30,0:03:04.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕是有一点点线索也好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.64,0:03:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的委托是调查邮件发信人的信息
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.35,0:03:15.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再往后就不属于我的工作范围了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.33,0:03:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.81,0:03:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把该做的都做了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.95,0:03:24.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就请你们按约定付报酬吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.90,0:03:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.32,0:03:27.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.74,0:03:32.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「日光浴食堂」的…春季展销会…通知
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.68,0:03:38.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现…现在正提供特别菜式…请试吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.92,0:03:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}凭此传单享受9折优惠
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.34,0:03:43.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.44,0:03:51.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了  你们挺努力的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.90,0:03:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,望月学姐  您也来一份吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.68,0:03:55.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.22,0:03:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会长  你在找人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.53,0:04:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.59,0:04:04.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.82,0:04:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女孩没见过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.33,0:04:17.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我们社团的新人  还请多照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.68,0:04:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问要不要试吃一下特别菜式
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.80,0:04:22.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是哪个学科的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.23,0:04:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几年级  名字叫什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.14,0:04:26.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  您这样我很为难
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.16,0:04:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了  京子小姐要去补妆了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.61,0:04:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我受够了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.24,0:04:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,京子小姐  你大受欢迎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.79,0:04:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全着了道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.67,0:04:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.69,0:04:46.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本打算做管家服的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.31,0:04:48.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不知不觉地做成女仆装了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.02,0:04:50.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么才能错成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.38,0:04:54.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法  谁都有犯错的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.38,0:04:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对是她们俩怂恿的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.55,0:05:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笕学长好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.50,0:05:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都想收进铃木世界遗产了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.93,0:05:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铃木  你在图书部开心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.23,0:05:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.58,0:05:12.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和大家在一起  给京子小姐化妆都开心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.50,0:05:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笕学长你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.74,0:05:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛  我个人感觉要是身高再矮20厘米就完美了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.43,0:05:24.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笕学长你也是乐在其中呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.78,0:05:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请闭一下眼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.57,0:05:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实际上我在图书部下了赌注
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.94,0:05:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望它能让我有所改变
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.27,0:05:50.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  让别人看见这样  会被误解的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.50,0:05:54.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算被误解  我觉得也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.85,0:05:58.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…如果我这么说  你会很困扰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.02,0:06:07.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.93,0:06:09.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白崎学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.86,0:06:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  御园同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.28,0:06:13.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.72,0:06:16.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  之前谢谢你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.26,0:06:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是送给你们大家的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.14,0:06:20.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.58,0:06:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎很辛苦呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.16,0:06:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是HAPPY  PROJECT吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.15,0:06:24.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.28,0:06:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  御园同学你要不要也来试试
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.82,0:06:30.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起来做这个的话其实很快乐的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.46,0:06:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  也就刚开始觉得害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.99,0:06:35.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.48,0:06:38.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有社交恐惧症  做不好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.73,0:06:41.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但御园同学你应该习惯站在众人面前了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.43,0:06:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  发现歌姬发传单的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.03,0:06:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家会很惊讶  也会很开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.31,0:06:50.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到底还是因为我是歌姬吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.99,0:06:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御园同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.81,0:06:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们会照顾生病的我  也是为了这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.13,0:06:57.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.53,0:06:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.10,0:07:04.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御园同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.27,0:07:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笕同学  怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.24,0:07:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}（放学后有新世界在等着你  牧羊人）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.40,0:07:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这都是骗人的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.91,0:07:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  御园同学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.48,0:07:27.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  你干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.12,0:07:33.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.09,0:07:37.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学长？  你有女装的兴趣吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.44,0:07:42.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不不  这是为了发传单  迫不得已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.47,0:07:44.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那您有什么事么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.93,0:07:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你不要误解白崎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.53,0:07:48.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没误解
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.12,0:07:52.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白崎是放不下你  才照顾你的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.76,0:07:53.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.69,0:07:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你相信白崎的善意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.11,0:08:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,善意是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.01,0:08:04.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学长你相信吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.21,0:08:05.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.56,0:08:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前也不相信
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.67,0:08:16.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾觉得那都是伪善
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.14,0:08:20.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我感觉白崎不同
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.85,0:08:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和她在一起是不会无聊的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.42,0:08:27.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她真是很不一般
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.16,0:08:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学长你的样子更不一般
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.00,0:08:37.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.58,0:08:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御园同学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.93,0:08:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  我太不注意了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.92,0:08:56.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.56,0:09:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  该道歉的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.13,0:09:04.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御园同学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.12,0:09:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话  御园同学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.91,0:09:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请…请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.78,0:09:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看  歌姬在发传单
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.73,0:09:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是  但为什么是猫耳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.74,0:09:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.64,0:09:30.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「日光浴食堂」要举办春季展销会
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.57,0:09:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好累
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.35,0:09:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御园同学  今天谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.95,0:09:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了你我们非常开心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.21,0:09:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.30,0:09:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  明天放学后来图书馆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.44,0:09:49.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.94,0:09:52.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有只非常有个性的猫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.63,0:09:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫！？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.80,0:09:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  那货算是猫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.46,0:10:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笕学长你把仪左大人当什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.73,0:10:03.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会考虑的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.51,0:10:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.93,0:10:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这气氛是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.33,0:10:26.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你别这样啊  佳奈助
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.30,0:10:29.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我们还以为是御园同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.23,0:10:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过佳奈助这叫法挺好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.23,0:10:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs18}注：在女人名字后面加『助』，表示对该女人的蔑视，在现代已经成为死语
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.37,0:10:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.78,0:10:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢  那以后就叫你佳奈助了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.81,0:10:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佳奈助
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.07,0:10:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佳奈助
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.45,0:10:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小佳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.50,0:10:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这方面你还真是坚持
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.67,0:10:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按喜欢的叫就好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.99,0:10:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧  蛋蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.99,0:10:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs18}注：玉和蛋发音同为tama
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.78,0:10:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你是活得不耐烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.15,0:10:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御园同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.77,0:10:56.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来看猫了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.88,0:10:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.22,0:11:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你能来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.82,0:11:06.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锵  这就是仪左大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.94,0:11:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仪左别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.33,0:11:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御园同学会吓…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.40,0:11:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.45,0:11:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.78,0:11:16.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,福利福利
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.49,0:11:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然还献媚  真不像话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.94,0:11:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不介意的话就用这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.01,0:11:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依照你的印象  绣了猫和音符
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.73,0:11:27.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.08,0:11:30.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是因为你是歌姬才…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.13,0:11:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.15,0:11:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的茶是专门为你调配的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.43,0:11:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对嗓子好  能让声音…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.89,0:11:41.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}乖乖
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.57,0:11:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小玉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.43,0:11:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是白崎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.71,0:11:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉我还介意这事就太傻了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.81,0:11:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.78,0:11:52.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小太刀同学  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.72,0:11:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们注意点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.70,0:11:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又多了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.08,0:11:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.25,0:12:00.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就当是赔礼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.47,0:12:03.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起去这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.62,0:12:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}（日出澡堂  优惠券）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.16,0:12:05.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打7折…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.36,0:12:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要去澡堂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.57,0:12:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥生寮的热水管道坏了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.41,0:12:19.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  每个房间都没有热水
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.71,0:12:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是昨晚的弥生寮里女生的黄色悲鸣接连不断…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.77,0:12:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算如此  为什么会发展成大家一起去泡澡呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.37,0:12:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能让图书部成员加深感情  不是挺好的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.86,0:12:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  笕你喜欢哪一个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.73,0:12:53.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么话题会变成这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.44,0:12:56.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有罪！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.05,0:12:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,判决书正文如下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.54,0:13:01.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小太刀凪的胸部颠覆了社会常识
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.72,0:13:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此有罪！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.16,0:13:03.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.31,0:13:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有异议！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.20,0:13:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有异议！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.02,0:13:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有异议！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.44,0:13:09.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜  正义的状况好悲惨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.46,0:13:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸部的状况好凄凉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.17,0:13:13.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要这么说的话那边的也有罪吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.10,0:13:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.11,0:13:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白崎学姐的仅擦过犯罪界线
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.02,0:13:18.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以是无罪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.69,0:13:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要哭了  铃木
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.03,0:13:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说白了只是脂肪块而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.23,0:13:26.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小佳每天都有喝牛奶吃肉  所以没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.83,0:13:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得你们两位的安慰只会起到反效果…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.14,0:13:31.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御园同学！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.02,0:13:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同志就是懂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.60,0:13:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不是你同志
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.95,0:13:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同为一年级生  让我们好好相处吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.14,0:13:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白崎  你又变大了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.23,0:13:43.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小玉  不要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.50,0:13:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早知道就带可以在洗澡时看的书来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.62,0:13:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用来保持你的理性吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.78,0:13:51.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要说傻话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.08,0:13:54.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.13,0:13:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道就好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.29,0:14:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄金周马上就要到了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.07,0:14:03.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.51,0:14:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于HAPPY  PROJECT的事  决定好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.14,0:14:09.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.44,0:14:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.60,0:14:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.88,0:14:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小太刀你跟笕很要好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.02,0:14:19.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说  说得是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.37,0:14:23.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们对笕感兴趣吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.08,0:14:25.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.26,0:14:28.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀  这气氛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.19,0:14:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是呢~  感觉书才是笕的女朋友呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.46,0:14:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家里到处都是书
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.84,0:14:37.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去过笕学长的家了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.32,0:14:40.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  笕没跟你们说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.07,0:14:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们两个的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.44,0:14:45.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说已经发展到那种地步了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.54,0:14:47.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大丑闻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.91,0:14:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌啦  我们只是邻居而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.13,0:14:58.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然他跟我说随时可以来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.22,0:15:00.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但去了也只是两人一起看深夜连续剧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.34,0:15:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  我先出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.36,0:15:08.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随时可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.97,0:15:10.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人到深夜…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.11,0:15:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笕学长
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.31,0:15:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有罪！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.90,0:15:17.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.14,0:15:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快就能迎来笕跟某人在一起的那天了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.72,0:15:22.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有种不舒畅的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.20,0:15:26.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.32,0:15:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗完澡的女孩子  真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.14,0:15:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去别的地方玩吧  高峰学长
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.09,0:15:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正笕学长好像在家里更快活
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.21,0:15:47.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笕同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.04,0:15:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有话想对你说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.10,0:15:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.54,0:15:56.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.47,0:15:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.37,0:16:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想说的话是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.81,0:16:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  明天你能给我答复吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.96,0:16:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  你指那件事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.97,0:16:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无论如何都想跟你谈一谈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.19,0:16:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前你问我的  想要改变自己的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.77,0:16:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还没有告诉你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.09,0:16:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我呢  有一个叫纱依的妹妹  她小我两岁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.69,0:16:28.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但一直生病住院
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.70,0:16:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可能去不了汐美学园了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.82,0:16:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没有那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.11,0:16:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就能治好病  一起上学的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.49,0:16:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐美学园是一个怎样的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.52,0:16:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一个非常好的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.59,0:16:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都过得非常开心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.52,0:16:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也结识了好多朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.58,0:16:51.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想早点介绍给你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.99,0:16:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前一阵子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.15,0:16:55.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社团里举行了联欢会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.35,0:16:56.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.40,0:16:59.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情急之下就撒了谎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.80,0:17:03.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想着尽量让纱依她打起精神来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.14,0:17:05.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就信口开河了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.42,0:17:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让纱依知道了事实肯定会失望的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.84,0:17:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只好继续圆谎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.49,0:17:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讨厌这样的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.17,0:17:20.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我非常没用
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.08,0:17:22.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很无语吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.32,0:17:29.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没用到可笑的地步了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.27,0:17:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.79,0:17:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.77,0:17:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.48,0:17:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白崎你是想在妹妹入学之前
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.07,0:17:39.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将谎言变成现实对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.74,0:17:42.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.48,0:17:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白崎  你很了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.73,0:17:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是在用实际行动一步步实现吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.30,0:17:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还完全不够呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.59,0:17:52.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在也还是单方面地接受着大家的帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.92,0:17:54.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因为白崎你在努力着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.83,0:17:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家才会想要帮助你的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.33,0:17:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿出自信吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.05,0:18:00.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笕同学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.89,0:18:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.05,0:18:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么白崎你想说的话都说完了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.45,0:18:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.40,0:18:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那明天在图书部再见
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.54,0:18:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管笕同学你给我怎样的答复
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.74,0:18:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都会接受的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.44,0:18:16.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.86,0:18:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也会认真作出答复的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.47,0:18:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过图书部的活动
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.34,0:18:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我了解到了白崎这个人的天性
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.39,0:18:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这几天里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.86,0:18:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都过得挺开心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.69,0:18:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.48,0:18:37.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.52,0:18:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生日快乐！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.04,0:18:46.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝贺你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.48,0:18:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝贺你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.86,0:18:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快到这边来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.75,0:18:59.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…为我准备的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.18,0:19:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是白崎的提议吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.79,0:19:04.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的  是大家一起想的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.05,0:19:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高峰记住了你的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.16,0:19:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚认识你的时候  不是交换学生证看了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.79,0:19:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大获成功
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.78,0:19:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笕学长  你现在的表情跟被豆子枪射过的鸽子一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.61,0:19:19.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.89,0:19:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起~唱！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.17,0:19:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Happy  birthday  to  you
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.91,0:19:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Happy  birthday  to  you
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.66,0:19:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.17,0:19:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑一笑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.97,0:19:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…想怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.85,0:19:40.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Happy  birthday  dear…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.21,0:19:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.90,0:19:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是…图书部的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.85,0:19:57.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Happy  birthday  to  you
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.33,0:20:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生日快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.85,0:20:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是  白崎的HAPPY  PROJECT吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.63,0:20:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笕学长  请表达一下你现在的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.14,0:20:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天真是太感谢各位了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.39,0:20:21.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺出乎意料的  让我吓了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.25,0:20:23.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.19,0:20:26.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.44,0:20:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  我想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.15,0:20:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这份感觉的真面目
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.66,0:20:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然增加了新的成员
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.13,0:20:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄金周过后也要多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.01,0:20:47.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笕同学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.79,0:20:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢发言！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.05,0:20:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笕同学  谢谢你！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.73,0:20:58.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次生日上得到他人发自内心的祝福
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.18,0:21:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全没有想到自己会迎来这样的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.91,0:21:08.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起「高兴」「愉快」之类的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.61,0:21:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反而是另一种完全未知的感情存在于我心中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.32,0:21:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这让我无所适从
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.38,0:21:18.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs18}收件人：牧羊人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.38,0:21:18.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs18}我要怎样才能跟你见面？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.46,0:21:23.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牧羊人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.23,0:21:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一切都在你的预料中吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.81,0:21:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs18\fad(0,1000)}发件人：牧羊人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.81,0:21:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs18\fad(0,1000)}为你新的启程献上祝福
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.81,0:21:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs18\fad(0,1000)}如果知道了我的真实身份就请来找我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.53,0:23:09.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仪左大人  今天请和我一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.07,0:23:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用拘谨
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.32,0:23:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.03,0:23:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.01,0:23:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我挠我挠我挠我挠
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.68,0:23:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘻嘻  不像话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.78,0:23:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还想要更多吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.04,0:23:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,PLEASE！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.21,0:23:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御园女王说的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.08,0:23:27.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须服从！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.29,0:23:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,调教！？
